      "value": "1.1  Social Behaviour Change Campaign (SBCC)1.2  River Clean Up campaigns1.3  Advocacy and policy advise to improve waste management in Nepal, share lessons learned and promote replication of the project in Nepal and other SACEP member states.1.4     Awareness raising campaign and training targeted at IWWs to promote safe collection and fair market price sale of UBC plastics to aggregators (and IEC materials)1.5   Identification of vulnerable IWWs and support in accessing social protection schemes.1.6 Her Safety Training for existing aggregators and access to better WASH facility at work1.7 Provision of health insurance and occupational health and safety package to IWWs (PPE+ Insurance+ workshop)"
